h1_title: How to Unlock the Secret Ending (True Ending)
content: Entering the secret Bishui Cave in Chapter 5 is part of the Five Element Carts side quest that the Pale-Axe Stalwart will send you on. Taking down the five carts will grant you access to the frozen-over cave, where you'll have two more bosses to tackle to complete it.
promot:
This is an excerpt from the file 'How_to_Unlock_the_Secret_Ending_(True_Ending).md', within the main section titled 'How to Unlock the Secret Ending (True Ending)', specifically from the subsection 'Unlock and Complete Bishui Cave (Chapter 5)'.
The content is as follows:
Entering the secret Bishui Cave in Chapter 5 is part of the Five Element Carts side quest that the Pale-Axe Stalwart will send you on. Taking down the five carts will grant you access to the frozen-over cave, where you'll have two more bosses to tackle to complete it.
